title: WEDNESDAY 3/24 - Giant problems for Kyle Rudolph
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 3/24 - Giant problems for Kyle Rudolph
description:
Tight end Kyle Rudolph's (0:06) deal with the Giants up in the air as he may need surgery. Raiders QB Marcus Mariota (0:38) restructures his deal to stay with Las Vegas...Cardinals GM Steve Keim (1:03) talks about the signings of JJ Watt and AJ Green, and Jameis Winston (1:53) discusses what he learned from Drew Brees, while the Eagles (3:00) find a backup for Jalen Hurts
